      "role": "user",
      "content": "i see. so it's basically saying there could be these sneaky, unexpected costs that crawl out of nowhere if something goes wrong? it feels a bit like there are traps buried in the wording that you can't really see until you're already in trouble. are there any other ways these clauses can be deceptive or act like \"hidden\" risks?",
